<section id="faq" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2 class="fade-in">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="fade-in">Get answers to common questions about AKADEMI TVET UNIRAZAK</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-content">
      <div class="faq-categories">
        <div class="category-tabs">
          <button class="tab-btn active" data-category="general">General Information</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" data-category="programs">Programs & Training</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" data-category="admission">Admission & Requirements</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" data-category="facilities">Facilities & Support</button>
        </div>

        <!-- General Information -->
        <div class="faq-category active" data-category="general">
          <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What is Akademi TVET UNIRAZAK (ATUR)?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>ATUR is an accredited training centre under the Department of Skills Development (JPK), Ministry of Human Resources. Established in September 2023, it offers skill-based programs from SKM Level 3 to DKM Level 4 for school leavers, working adults, and industry professionals.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What awards has ATUR received?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Malaysia's Best Accredited Centre</strong> – Administrative Management (2024)</li>
                  <li><strong>Outstanding Personality Award</strong> – Azlin Shah Zainal Abidin (TVET Education)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>Are the programs recognized nationally?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes. All programs are accredited by JPK under the Malaysian Skills Certification (SKM/DKM) and recognized under the Malaysian Qualifications Framework (MQF).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Programs & Training -->
        <div class="faq-category" data-category="programs">
          <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What types of programs are offered?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>ATUR offers three types of programs:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Institution-Based Training (SLAPB):</strong> Full-time learning at the academy</li>
                  <li><strong>Industry-Based Training (SLDN):</strong> Dual training at the academy and industry workplace</li>
                  <li><strong>Recognition of Prior Learning (PB-PPT / PPA-PPT):</strong> Assessment-based certification for experienced workers</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What are the programs available under SLAPB (Institution-Based Training)?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul>
                  <li>Administrative Management (FB025-4:2012)</li>
                  <li>Early Childhood Education (T982-001-4:2018)</li>
                  <li>Graphic Design (Digital) (IT-058-3:2014)</li>
                  <li>Creative Content Development (IT-070-4:2011)</li>
                  <li>Computer System Administration (IT-020-4:2013)</li>
                  <li>Preschool Education (P854-009-4:2020)</li>
                  <li>Aesthetic Services (S960-002-3:2020)</li>
                  <li>Mutawif Management - Umrah & Ziarah (N791-001-4:2016)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Each program offers either SKM Level 3, DKM Level 4, or both (Single-Tier or Multi-Tier).</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What are the durations of the programs?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>SKM Level 3:</strong> 1 – 1.8 years</li>
                  <li><strong>DKM Level 4 (Single-Tier):</strong> 2 – 2.8 years</li>
                  <li><strong>DKM Level 4 (Multi-Tier):</strong> Varies depending on prior qualifications</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What is the learning approach?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>80% Practical and 20% Theory</strong></li>
                  <li>Delivered by experienced trainers, many with >10 years experience and professional qualifications</li>
                  <li>Uses Learning Management System (LMS) and URAPP Student Portal</li>
                  <li>Simulated environments (e.g., mock office, mock preschool, computer lab)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What is the PPA-PPT / PB-PPT program?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>These are Recognition of Prior Learning (RPL) programs for experienced professionals:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Certification is based on a portfolio or practical assessment</li>
                  <li>Must meet NOSS criteria and have sufficient years of work experience</li>
                  <li>No need to attend full-time classes</li>
                  <li>Suitable for those aged 21+ (depending on level)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Admission & Requirements -->
        <div class="faq-category" data-category="admission">
          <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What are the entry requirements?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul>
                  <li>Malaysian citizen</li>
                  <li>Aged between 15 to 35 years</li>
                  <li>Able to read, write, and count</li>
                  <li>SPM leavers and working adults are encouraged</li>
                  <li>Must be physically and mentally fit</li>
                  <li>Must have an interest in the program applied</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>Is financial assistance available?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes. Students can apply for PTPK (Tabung Pembangunan Kemahiran), which covers:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Study fees</li>
                  <li>Transportation</li>
                  <li>Living allowances</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What are the career opportunities after graduation?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Graduates can pursue careers such as:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>TVET Lecturer or Trainer</li>
                  <li>Executive Secretary / Admin Officer</li>
                  <li>Early Childhood Teacher or Supervisor</li>
                  <li>Graphic Designer, Web Designer, or Photographer</li>
                  <li>Network Administrator or Computer Technician</li>
                  <li>Entrepreneur or business owner in respective fields</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Facilities & Support -->
        <div class="faq-category" data-category="facilities">
          <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>Is hostel accommodation provided?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes. Students can stay at Residensi Teratai in Danau Kota, KL:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms per unit</li>
                  <li>Max 10 pax per unit</li>
                  <li>Facilities: gym, self-laundry, swimming pool, shuttle bus</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>What activities or support are available to students?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <ul>
                  <li>Orientation and registration day</li>
                  <li>Career guidance and industrial training placement</li>
                  <li>School of Happiness, Library, Computer Labs</li>
                  <li>Simulation rooms and practical exposure</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item fade-in">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <h4>Who should I contact for more information?</h4>
                <div class="faq-toggle">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="contact-info-faq">
                  <h5>Education Counsellors:</h5>
                  <div class="contact-methods-faq">
                    <div class="contact-method-faq">
